<h2>Why is Mclaren the second best?</h2>
<p> Mclaren is the second best team within Formula 1, because of their team itself. The people all have a great sense of humour, 
  and they are actually alright when they lose, because they hardly win. It's also just fun to support Mclaren, as they are very
  unserious throughout most of their races.
</p>

